  "time_ut": 1660873675,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b90.\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Minister of Energy lodged a complaint with the CIT",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekara has filed a complaint with the Criminal Investigation Department against the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation and the Sri Lanka Petroleum Storage Terminal Corporation.",
        "He said that he has filed a complaint demanding that inquiries be made regarding the activities of the companies concerned in relation to fuel purchase, evaluation of recommendations, non-supply of fuel to those who have booked, selection of distributors and distribution system."
      ],
